  "detailed_description": "<h1>ROGUE MASTERS COMMUNITY</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063590/extras/bc51de5273bc2aa478fe3a8c0d1a0ba4.avif?t=1768051617\" width=600 height=72 /></span><br>A civilization that lacks Willpower is doomed to collapse against Entropy, the force responsible for corrupting the universe. Cooperate with up to 6 warriors and use your Willpower to fight against waves of increasingly stronger creatures until you reach the Champion of Entropy, an extremely powerful foe you’ll prove your worth against.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063590/extras/86e6318ac783fd4a4eb900fbc4defebc.poster.avif?t=1768051617\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063590/extras/86e6318ac783fd4a4eb900fbc4defebc.webm?t=1768051617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063590/extras/86e6318ac783fd4a4eb900fbc4defebc.mp4?t=1768051617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063590/extras/5c88ea73d7dfde9ec457b5781e7a435a.avif?t=1768051617\" width=600 height=72 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fight Entropy with up to 6 players in a horde survival gameplay against increasingly powerful enemies.</li><li>Choose the right weapons for each situation and master the souls-like combat.</li><li>Build your character through a wide variety of equipments to suit your playstyle.</li><li>Customize your appearance through an extensive transmogrification system.</li><li>Host your own room or find one to join in the server list, along with the connection quality to the host (the game uses Peer-to-Peer connections so there are no dedicated servers).</li><li>Offline solo mode available so you can play however you want.</li><li>NO microtransactions - everything is acquired through gameplay.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063590/extras/0ee0e25b50651b3bf2332edd0bc1c447.poster.avif?t=1768051617\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063590/extras/0ee0e25b50651b3bf2332edd0bc1c447.webm?t=1768051617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063590/extras/0ee0e25b50651b3bf2332edd0bc1c447.mp4?t=1768051617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063590/extras/bc51de5273bc2aa478fe3a8c0d1a0ba4.avif?t=1768051617\" width=600 height=72 /></span><br>A civilization that lacks Willpower is doomed to collapse against Entropy, the force responsible for corrupting the universe. Cooperate with up to 6 warriors and use your Willpower to fight against waves of increasingly stronger creatures until you reach the Champion of Entropy, an extremely powerful foe you’ll prove your worth against.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063590/extras/86e6318ac783fd4a4eb900fbc4defebc.poster.avif?t=1768051617\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063590/extras/86e6318ac783fd4a4eb900fbc4defebc.webm?t=1768051617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063590/extras/86e6318ac783fd4a4eb900fbc4defebc.mp4?t=1768051617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063590/extras/5c88ea73d7dfde9ec457b5781e7a435a.avif?t=1768051617\" width=600 height=72 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fight Entropy with up to 6 players in a horde survival gameplay against increasingly powerful enemies.</li><li>Choose the right weapons for each situation and master the souls-like combat.</li><li>Build your character through a wide variety of equipments to suit your playstyle.</li><li>Customize your appearance through an extensive transmogrification system.</li><li>Host your own room or find one to join in the server list, along with the connection quality to the host (the game uses Peer-to-Peer connections so there are no dedicated servers).</li><li>Offline solo mode available so you can play however you want.</li><li>NO microtransactions - everything is acquired through gameplay.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063590/extras/0ee0e25b50651b3bf2332edd0bc1c447.poster.avif?t=1768051617\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063590/extras/0ee0e25b50651b3bf2332edd0bc1c447.webm?t=1768051617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063590/extras/0ee0e25b50651b3bf2332edd0bc1c447.mp4?t=1768051617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
